epresents a one-dimensional shape located at a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"single geographical coordinate. Depending on how it is used, an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" object is known as a point annotation or point shape. For"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"example, you could use a point shape to represent a city at low zoom levels, an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"address at high zoom levels, or the location of a long press gesture."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointAnnotation"}}}